    <stitle>13 SPEED AND 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-713/18 SERIES - REMOVE - GEAR SHIFT LEVER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="2">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Remote control housings are removed the same way as gear shift levers.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the four (4) retaining bolts from the gear shift lever base (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300713">Figure 13</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300713" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300713" filename="../figg13/G1300713.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 13. Remove Retaining Bolts From Gear Shift Lever Base</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To break the gasket seal, lightly jar the gear shift housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300713">Figure 13</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the gear shift lever housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300714">Figure 14</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300714" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300714" filename="../figg13/G1300714.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 14. Remove Gear Shift Lever Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the gasket and clean all mounting surfaces of gasket material (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300714">Figure 14</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
